description:
On today’s show, Dr. Emily is bringing you a Sex With Emily year in review! She’s doing a quick overview of the top guests, blogs, and moments from 2019. 

 

She discusses the topics that all of you listeners were the most interested in over the year, what blogs helped get your sex lives on track, and the podcasts and guests you all couldn’t get enough of this year. Let’s hear it for 2019 and get off to a great start in 2020!

  

Follow Emily on all social @sexwithemily

For even more sex advice, tips & tricks, visit sexwithemily.com
